Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he doesn't wanna live with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I annoying to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I know?! Think for yourself!\NI gotta leave this country already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only came here to ask\N"Are you really okay with things this way?"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not okay with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you wanna come with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Bond Between Father and Daughter!\NKyros and Rebecca!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate is a pirate after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never trust a pirate again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you were a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of Rebecca-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Free her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our target is Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now, Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's go!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Sea Prism Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up the princess without a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Get on!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoa! What's going on?!\N--Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's my meat!\N--I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave you behind the hill and lure them away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So go off on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole nation is trying to protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get caught, they'll take you back to the Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh! But where should I go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier is at the small house\Nin the Flower Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flower Field?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta hurry or he'll be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! But don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyros, hold her in your arms.\NShe's your daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't touch such an innocent thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hands are tainted!\NI don't wanna taint her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're like an angel, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be watching over you!\NI'll always be by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute she is! How cute she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.21,0:08:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crying again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Scarlet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I fulfilled my role.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forgive me for telling a lie about your husband.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I did it all so that Rebecca can live a happy life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother-{\i1}sama{\i0}, I picked so many flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wow, Rebecca!\N--Would you like to have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I would like to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is from your mother to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sold all the flowers today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we did. Maybe people bought them\Nbecause you're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You helped your mother!\NGood girl, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to the palace!\NAlright, Scarlet? Rebecca?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I couldn't protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't protect your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I couldn't protect your mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:11:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna protect you to the end,\Nwith my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like you, Soldier-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nbecause you couldn't protect my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this warmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's much warmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soldier-san is a brave man{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He will always be by your side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... haven't told you... told you anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rebecca...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live with you one day,\Nin the same house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me teach you how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother said I shouldn't hurt anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna teach you how to not get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:03.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you were a member of the royal family,\Nyou've been running around,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:05.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,getting insulted for a decade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why, this time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you to have your chance at happiness\Nas a member of the royal family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't stay here, either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, about the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.57,0:13:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a worthless guy who fought all the time\Nin the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whatever the reason was,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:14:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really killed people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a daughter of some prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anyone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if he killed hundreds of people\Nor how tainted his hands are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only have one father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kyros' daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the day you are filled with happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will always be by your side!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay by my side like you promised, Soldier-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it okay with you that I'm your father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's live together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca will never come back here,\NFather-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:16:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola... I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Viola-{\i1}san{\i0}!\NBut could you take my place and become a princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Viola!\NBut could you take my place and become a princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis-{\i1}sama{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the second time in my life\Nthat someone asked me such an odd favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Rebecca is really like her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy isn't here yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar Law's not here, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:36.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE RUINS OF THE FOREST TOWN - CARTA\NTHE EAST PORT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are both of our bosses doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some enemies that can't be held back\Neven by us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujitora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The unwanted one's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fools rush in where angels fear to tread"-{\i1}dara{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already sent reinforcements\Nto the east port where Straw Hat's heading!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The warships on the sea\Nand Issho-{\i1}san{\i0} will pincer them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll catch the Straw Hats and the other criminals\Nin one fell swoop-{\i1}dara{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-Wh-What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We only have one choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and your friends should stand back!\NLeave it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Up to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What happened to the reinforcements\Nfor the east port-{\i1}dara{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, sir!\NWell, most of the units became incapacitated¬Åc{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean-{\i1}dara{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The bullets and gunpowder are missing\Nfrom their rifles!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And all their other weapons like\Nswords, pistols, axes, spears, and knives...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...went missing, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They must've been stolen...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And at the port,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:35.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the warships are stuck together\Nas if they got sewn to one another
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:37.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,so they can't sail out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could the iron be sewn together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the string! Cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't have a knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, the soldiers who suddenly collapsed\Nare still paralyzed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you idiots?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna let the Straw Hats and the other criminals walk away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W-We'll do our best!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay to get this much healing properties today,\NMouji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The donors will be paralyzed\Nif we take too much out of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! We got permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Kyros-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do as I say, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Then, I won't hesitate!\NWe still have so many heavily-injured people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're in the middle of it\Nbut we gotta go...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be finished soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,THROB
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to the citizens,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}all these strange occurrences are\Nthe work of fairies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Cut the fairy crap-{\i1}dara{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I-I-I'm sorry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will your barrier work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were breakable,\Nit wouldn't be called a barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep holding on\Nuntil Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0} and Trafalgar come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they fighting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NAVY BRAND RICE CRACKERS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some rice crackers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.26,0:20:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks. Just start talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boy with White Lead Disease?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there was a survivor\Nfrom the White Town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He hates everything in this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Feels like I'm watching my older brother\Nwhen he was a kid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel sorry for him but there's no way to\Ncure White Lead Disease.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't get involved too much\Nor you'll give yourself away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to stop my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo is a violent man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let him go to Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, a Navy soldier died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was someone special to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met him when he was a kid\Nand I thought of him as my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was honest and\Nhad a stronger sense of justice than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was a subordinate that I could trust as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he lied to me just once in his lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you have a deal regarding\Nthe Op-Op Fruit?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! But it's top secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cora-san must be talking to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be it for Doflamingo!\NWe'll ambush at Swallow Island
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.11,0:22:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and catch the Donquixote Family\Nin one fell swoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.07,0:22:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay away from the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the landing unit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is an executive of the Donquixote Family\Namong the dead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.62,0:22:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His code name: Corazon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.67,0:22:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,JUSTICE OVER ALL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've sent a picture of him.\NCould you confirm?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rosinante!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why were you there on the island?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.32,0:22:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he must've had a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four things were lost during that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrels Pirates. My subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:22:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Op-Op Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:23:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the boy who was with the Donquixote Family\Nat the time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.09,0:23:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who was suffering from White Lead Disease!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.68,0:23:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.61,0:23:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Admiral Fujitora, with his overwhelming strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stands in the way of the Straw Hats and the others who are trying to escape!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:32.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Luffy fights against him with all his power
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:34.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and his firm resolve to become the King of the Pirates!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.94,0:23:37.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the two men's inflexible determinations collide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.68,0:23:40.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with each other, their all-out special attacks crackle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.54,0:23:45.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Men's Pride! Luffy vs. Fujitora, Head-to-Head!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.46,0:23:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
